url: "https://yoontf0.github.io/safeguard-mmwave-simulator/"
license: MIT
keywords:
  - embedded systems
  - child presence detection
  - UWB
  - mmWave
  - Raspberry Pi
  - Cascading Wake-up
  - Streamlit
  - simulation
